&lt;li&gt;Ensure every end user is fully onboarded, trained, and actively using the product&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor usage and adoption metrics — flag anything that looks off before it becomes a problem&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run regular working-level meetings with the customer&#39;s operational team, always with an agenda and a clear purpose&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
